post.description:
Here you can create a brand new Workspace.

**Note**: Only [Organization](https://starkbank.com/docs/api#workspace:~:text=Note%3A%20Only-,Organization,-credentials%20are%20able) credentials are able to create Workspaces.

tags.name: Boleto
tags.description:
A boleto is a method you can use to charge your customers or load your Stark Bank account. Here we will teach you how to create and manage boletos.

You can also split a Boleto between different receivers, you need to create a [Split Receiver](#split-receiver), and add the receiver into the Splits array.

tags.name: Transfer
tags.description:
Transfers are used to send money to any bank account in Brazil using the TED or Pix systems.
Here we will show you how to create and manage them.
